FACILITY CLOSURE EFFECTIVE TUESDAY
Anacortes Public Library will close indefinitely starting Tuesday, March 17. This includes the Community Meeting Room & Study Rooms. Staff will be available Monday-Friday via phone and online to assist with digital access and account information. All holds & checkouts are suspended. Please keep the materials you have checked out with you for the duration of the library closure.
Limited access:
Library staff will be available 11:00am-5:30pm via phone and online, Monday-Friday to assist with digital access and account queries during the building closure. Hoopla checkouts are extended to 10 items a month with support from the Library Foundation. Overdrive/Libby, Linda, Mango, and more are available using your library account via online access for digital books, audio books, online tutorials, movies, music and more.
